Template for scroll-driven navigation map, as used in Star-Ledger’s Forgotten Shore project: 

http://data.nsl.webfactional.com/sandbox/spitetest.html

This map was adapted from Mapbox’s Sherlock Holmes tutorial, “The Adventure of the Bruce Partington Plans: 

https://www.mapbox.com/mapbox.js/example/v1.0.0/scroll-driven-navigation/

NOTE: May need to be updated to accommodate changes to Mapbox.js

